						<div class="postbody">Who needs macros when you can do this?<br /><br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">; typedef struct { /*<br />.struct MyStruct ; */<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; ; byte Abc; /*<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; Abc .byte ; */<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; ; byte Def; /*<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; Def .word ; */<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; ; unsigned char color; /* <br />.endstruct ;*/ } pixel_t;<br /></div><br /><br />Requires your C compiler to allow empty ';' statements though.</div>

